te":"February 20, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, make what is within me better than my outward appearance and make my outward appearance righteous. O Allah, I ask You for the righteousness of what You give to people of property, family,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24240,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/01\/04\/ibn-masud-misguiding-trials\/","url_meta":{"origin":22482,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Fitnah: Seek refuge in Allah from misguiding trials","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 4, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Qurtubi reported: Ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cDo not say: O Allah, fortify me from trials. Indeed, not one of you returns to his family and children but that it is included among the trials. Rather, say: O Allah, I seek refuge in you from trials\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25369,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/30\/adorn-us-beauty-iman\/","url_meta":{"origin":22482,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Iman: O Allah, adorn us with the beauty of faith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 30, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ammar ibn Yasar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u20